172 A.3d 1086 FISHER, KRYSTAL AND DAVID, PLAINTIFFS-PETITIONERS, v. CITY OF MILLVILLE, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-267 September Term 2017

079748 November 9, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003351-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
